<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>untuk anai 🤍</title>

<style>
body{
margin:0;
background:#111;
color:white;
font-family:Arial;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
height:100vh;
text-align:center;
}

.card{
max-width:500px;
padding:20px;
background:#1c1c1c;
border-radius:20px;
}

img{
width:200px;
border-radius:15px;
margin:10px 0;
}

button{
padding:12px 25px;
border:none;
border-radius:20px;
background:#ff4d6d;
color:white;
cursor:pointer;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="card">
<h2>💌 untuk anai</h2>

<img src="foto.jpg" alt="foto">

<br>

<button onclick="document.getElementById('musik').play(); document.getElementById('t').style.display='block'">
klik di sini
</button>

<p id="t" style="display:none;margin-top:15px;line-height:1.6">
hai anai...<br><br>
aku cuma mau bilang kalau aku masih inget kamu.<br>
dan semua hal yang pernah kita lewatin.<br><br>
🤍
</p>

<audio id="musik" loop>
<source src="musik.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
</audio>

</div>

</body>
</html>
